<s> OK you asked for it.  </s>
<s> I right click why wonderful HTML file I have just been writing from any folder on the hard drive and "Send To" my batch file in the same folder as the "tidy.exe"  </s>
<s> (and config.txt for that matter) download I got many months ago.  </s>
<s> ------------Start of batch file -------------- find /v /n "" %1  %1_num.txt  </s>
<s> copy %1 "%1_newver.htm"  </s>
<s> tidy.exe -config config.txt  </s>
<s> -f %1_notes.txt  </s>
<s> -modify "%1_newver.htm"  </s>
<s> -----------End of batch file ----------------- ----------- to set up right click --------------------- 1 .  </s>
